OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSackler family wins        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fimmunity from opioid       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Flawsuits                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The billionaire owners of Purdue Pharma
OL,6, will be protected from lawsuits linked 
OL,7, to the US opioid crisis in exchange for
OL,8, a $6bn (#4.85bn) settlement.           
OL,10,FPurdue, which filed for bankruptcy in  
OL,11,F2019 amid thousands of lawsuits, made  
OL,12,Fdrugs like OxyContin and is blamed for 
OL,13,Ffuelling the crisis.                   
OL,15,FOn Tuesday, an appeals court ruled that
OL,16,Fits owners, the Sackler family, would  
OL,17,Freceive full immunity from civil suits.
OL,19,FIn exchange, they will pay $6bn to help
OL,20,Faddress opioid addiction.              
